Numpad 1: Rapid Recovery - You will very quickly recover from your injuries.  High falls and ectremely devestating events may still kill you.
Numpad 2: Levitation Kill - which ever character is in your focus will be instantly thrown 20 feet into the air and will most likely land with enough force to be killed.
Numpad 3: Save Position - Save your current position.
Numpad 4: Teleport - Telport to saved position.
Numpad 5: Undo Teleport - Undo your teleport.
Numpad 6: Assassin Jump - Your assassin will instantly shoot 6 to 10 feet into the air.  Be careful of long falls and where you are jumping!

Numpad 7: Assasin Blend - Your HUD indicator will show you as Un-noticed, and those whom you attack will not be able to see you or fight back.  Enemies or characters that already have seen you will continue to attack.  It's best to activate this function before you are spotted or attacked.
Numpad 8: Unlimited Throwing Knives- You have 30 knives and as long as this is activated, they will not decrease when you throw them.
Numpad 9: Add Time to Timer- Adds more time to the timed events.
